# Business Model — AffiPartner Morocco

> **For AI agents:** This file is the source of truth for business logic.
> Before changing products, pricing, commissions, orders, or roles — read this fully.
> Cross-check changes against `constraints.mdc` (what NOT to build).
> See `docs/RISK_APPROVAL_MATRIX.md` for actions requiring user approval.

## Platform identity
Morocco-focused affiliate + wholesale B2B platform. Primary currency: **MAD**.
Allowed purchase currencies: MAD, USD, AED (convert to MAD via exchange_rate_to_mad).

## Two user flows

### 1. Affiliate COD (Cash on Delivery)
- Affiliate shares a referral link `/products/[id]?ref=[affiliateId]`
- Customer places a COD order (name, phone, city, address, quantity)
- Platform confirms, sources, ships via a Morocco delivery company
- Delivery company collects COD cash from customer, remits to platform after delay
- Commission recorded at delivery, payable only after COD received and verified
- **Affiliates set their own selling price** — platform does not control final customer price
- Platform earns: `sell_price - cost_price - operational_fees` per order
- Affiliate earns: `commission_amount` (fixed per product, paid after delivery)

### 2. Wholesale / B2B
- Wholesale buyer adds products to cart, submits via WhatsApp
- Admin confirms order manually, creates internal wholesale order
- Tier pricing applies based on quantity (min 10 units)
- Standard tiers: 10+ pcs: cost+30%, 50+ pcs: cost+25%, 100+ pcs: cost+20%, 500+ pcs: cost+15%
- All wholesale prices rounded to whole MAD (no decimals)
- `import_on_demand` products are B2B/wholesale only — no affiliate access

## Product availability types
| Type | Affiliates | Wholesale | Origin |
|---|---|---|---|
| `local_stock` | ✅ if affiliate_enabled | ✅ | locally_produced OR imported_but_in_morocco_stock |
| `import_on_demand` | ❌ always | ✅ | imported, sourced per order |

## Operational costs per order (tracked separately)
- `confirmation_fee_mad` — cost of confirming the order (default 10 MAD)
- `packaging_fee_mad` — packaging cost (default 10 MAD)
- `delivery_fee_mad` — delivery company fee estimate (default 0, set per product)

## Commission model
- `commission_amount` on `products` = fixed MAD paid to affiliate per delivered order
- Commission status: `pending` → `approved` → `paid`
- Dashboard shows: earned total, paid total, pending balance (earned - paid)

## Roles
- `admin` — full access, approves products and orders
- `affiliate` — sees only affiliate-enabled products, their own orders + commissions
- `wholesaler` — sees all active approved products, their own cart + wholesale orders
- `agent` — reserved for future operational agents
